text: @UPSHelp I ordered some trainers from the US and I live in the UK, I have received no shipping information but I know the company uses your service to ship. Could You help me?

@ThompsonJordan_ I can certainly assist. We will require your tracking number, address, phone number for further assistance. If you don't have this, I suggest contacting the company which shipped it. They will have it in their shipping history. ^ZM https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
